Package: tactile
Title: New and Extended Plots, Methods, and Panel Functions for 'lattice'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Johan", "Larsson", email = "johanlarsson@outlook.com",
                    role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Deepayan", "Sarkar", role = c("ctb", "cph"),
                    comment = "lattice"))
Description: This package's name, an anagram of 'lattice', extends the
  functionality of the 'lattice' package by providing new high-level functions,
  methods for existing functions, panel functions, and theme.
Depends:
  R (>= 3.4.0),
  lattice
